---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/PageLayout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "27 March 2026";
---

<PageLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of service for card.oriz.in — the rules and guidelines for using our website and services."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-text-tertiary">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          By accessing and using card.oriz.in ("the Website"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must not use the Website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          card.oriz.in provides information about credit cards, debit cards, and prepaid cards available in India. We offer comparison tools, calculators, AI-powered recommendations, and educational content related to personal finance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">3. Disclaimer — Card Information</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-text-primary">card.oriz.in is not a financial institution, bank, or card issuer.</strong> We do not issue credit cards, debit cards, or any financial products.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-4">
          While we strive to ensure all card information is accurate and up-to-date, we make no guarantees about the completeness, accuracy, or reliability of any information on the Website. Card fees, benefits, terms, and conditions are subject to change by the issuing banks without notice.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Always verify card details directly with the issuing bank before making any financial decisions. We are not responsible for any loss or damage resulting from reliance on information provided on this Website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">4. No Financial Advice</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          The content, tools, and recommendations on card.oriz.in are for informational purposes only and do not constitute financial, legal, or professional advice. You should consult with a qualified financial advisor before making decisions about credit products.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">5. Affiliate Links & Advertising</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Some links on card.oriz.in may be affiliate links. If you apply for a card through an affiliate link, we may receive a commission from the bank or partner. This does not affect our editorial independence — our rankings and recommendations are data-driven and not influenced by affiliate relationships.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">6. User Accounts</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          If you create an account on card.oriz.in, you are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all activities under your account. You must provide accurate information and update it as necessary.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          All content on card.oriz.in — including text, graphics, logos, data compilations, and software — is the property of card.oriz.in or its content providers and is protected by Indian and international copyright laws.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, card.oriz.in shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits or revenues, whether incurred directly or indirectly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the Website after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">10. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@card.oriz.in" class="text-gold hover:text-gold-2 transition-colors">legal@card.oriz.in</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
